# AIUnitTest

[![PyPI version](https://badge.fury.io/py/AIUnitTest.svg)](https://badge.fury.io/py/AIUnitTest)
[![Python versions](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/AIUnitTest.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/AIUnitTest)
